About the League

Foundation & Inagural Season: Our league was fouded circa 2007 in the dorms of Hassayampa at Arizona State by Ben C, Jon H, Yacine B & Zach Z.

*Historical Fun Fact: Current NBA player James Harden was a freshman living in the same dorm as our league during Season 1.
